177
00:19:47,621 --> 00:19:51,454
<font color="#ffff00">Berhenti, jangan pukul lagi…</font>

178
00:20:06,390 --> 00:20:08,030
<font color="#ffff00">Dao Ming-si.</font>

179
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:18,710
<font color="#ffff00">Dao Ming-si, kamu mau ke mana?
