185
00:20:58,190 --> 00:21:02,044
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan pergi. Dao Ming-si.</font>

186
00:21:11,825 --> 00:21:15,903
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan, jangan pergi…</font>

187
00:21:16,003 --> 00:21:19,332
<font color="#ffff00">Sudah bangun… Shan-cai./
