188
00:21:19,432 --> 00:21:21,389
<font color="#ffff00">Shan-cai.</font>

189
00:21:22,453 --> 00:21:25,479
<font color="#ffff00">Cepat…/ Ayo./ Baik.</font>

190
00:21:28,190 --> 00:21:33,070
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah. Ibu, aku di mana?/
