199
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:56,430
<font color="#ffff00">Shan-cai…</font>

200
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:03,030
<font color="#ffff00">Bodoh. Untuk apa kamu kemari?</font>

201
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:08,110
